Definition: physics) a deformation of an object in which parallel planes remain parallel but are shifted in a direction parallel to themselves
Example: the shear changed the quadrilateral into a parallelogram
Synonyms: noun, event, deformation, cognition, physics, c, a, of, an, object, in, which, parallel, planes, remain, but, are, shifted, direction, to, themselves, the, changed, quadrilateral, into, parallelogram
Category: noun.phenomenon
